# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# API Base URL
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Development (default — Vite proxy forwards /api to .NET):
#   Leave this commented out. The proxy in vite.config.ts handles it.
#
# Production (built frontend served by .NET on the same origin):
#   Also leave commented out — relative /api works automatically.
#
# Custom / standalone .NET server on a different port or host:
#   Uncomment and set the full URL:
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:4521/api